title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Day' game

maintext:
RICHMOND, Va. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Virginia Lottery’s “Pick 4 Day” game were:
8-8-6-6
(eight, eight, six, six)
